commit.message:
symbols/eventparttimer.xpm: modify symbol

On screen the symbols "eventparttimer" and "eventtimer" are hard to
distinguish. This patch gives "eventparttimer" a slighter and smaller
shape.

Signed-off-by: Martin Dummer <martin.dummer@gmx.net>
Get rid of channel locking issues.
Get rid of timer locking issues.
Updated German translation (Thanks to Andreas Brachold).

Added a new theme: Potato (Thanks to Andreas Brachold).
